@notice Check the manager's staked token balance in the pool.
 @return Token balance of the manager's stake.

devdoc.details: Extends Lender.       Extends ManagedLendingPool by inheritance.

amountDepositable().details: Return value depends on the pool state rather than caller's balance.

returns._0: Max amount of tokens depositable to the pool.

amountUnstakable().details: Return value depends on the manager's stake balance, and is limited by pool liquidity.

returns._0: Max amount of tokens unstakable by the manager.

amountWithdrawable().details: Return value depends on the callers balance, and is limited by pool liquidity.

returns._0: Max amount of tokens withdrawable by msg.sender.

approveLoan(uint256).details: Loan must be in APPLIED status.      Caller must be the manager.      Loan amount must not exceed poolLiquidity();      Stake to pool funds ratio must be good - poolCanLend() must be true.

params.wallet: Address of the wallet to check the balance of.

returns._0: Token balance of the wallet in this pool.
Token balance of the manager's stake.

borrow(uint256).details: Caller must be the borrower.       The loan must be in APPROVED status.

params.loanId: id of the loan to withdraw funds of.

cancelLoan(uint256).details: Loan must be in APPROVED status.      Caller must be the manager.

params.minLoanAmount: Minimum amount to be borrowed per loan.
params.protocol: Address of a wallet to accumulate protocol earnings.
params.tokenAddress: ERC20 token contract address to be used as main pool liquid currency.

defaultLoan(uint256).details: Loan must be in FUNDS_WITHDRAWN status.      Caller must be the manager.

denyLoan(uint256).details: Loan must be in APPLIED status.      Caller must be the manager.

deposit(uint256).details: Deposit amount must be non zero and not exceed amountDepositable().      An appropriate spend limit must be present at the token contract.      Caller must not be any of: manager, protocol, current borrower.

loanBalanceDue(uint256).details: Loan must be in FUNDS_WITHDRAWN status.

params.loanId: ID of the loan to check the balance of.

returns._0: Total amount due with interest on this loan.
True if the staked funds provide at least a minimum ratio to the pool funds, False otherwise.

protocolEarningsOf(address).details: This method is useful for manager and protocol addresses.       Calling this method for a non-protocol associated addresses will return 0.

params.wallet: Address of the wallet to check the earnings balance of.

returns._0: Accumulated earnings of the wallet from the protocol.

repay(uint256,uint256).details: Caller must be the borrower.      Loan must be in FUNDS_WITHDRAWN status.      Only the necessary sum is charged if amount exceeds amount due.      Amount charged will not exceed the amount parameter.

params.loanId: ID of the loan to make a payment towards.

returns._0: A pair of total amount changed including interest, and the interest charged.

requestLoan(uint256,uint256).details: Requested amount must be greater or equal to minAmount().      Loan duration must be between minDuration() and maxDuration().      Caller must not be a lender, protocol, or the manager.       Multiple pending applications from the same address are not allowed,      most recent loan/application of the caller must not have APPLIED status.

returns._0: ID of a new loan application.

setDefaultAPR(uint16).details: apr must be inclusively between SAFE_MIN_APR and SAFE_MAX_APR.      Caller must be the manager.

params.apr: Loan APR to be applied for the new loan requests.

setDefaultLateAPRDelta(uint16).details: lateAPRDelta must be inclusively between SAFE_MIN_APR and SAFE_MAX_APR.      Caller must be the manager.

params.lateAPRDelta: Loan late payment APR delta to be applied for the new loan requests.

setLoanMaxDuration(uint256).details: Duration must be in seconds and inclusively between SAFE_MIN_DURATION and SAFE_MAX_DURATION.      Caller must be the manager.

params.duration: Maximum loan duration to be enforced for the new loan requests.

setLoanMinDuration(uint256).details: Duration must be in seconds and inclusively between SAFE_MIN_DURATION and SAFE_MAX_DURATION.      Caller must be the manager.

params.duration: Maximum loan duration to be enforced for the new loan requests.

setMinLoanAmount(uint256).details: minLoanAmount must be greater than or equal to SAFE_MIN_AMOUNT.      Caller must be the manager.

params.minLoanAmount: minimum loan amount to be enforced for the new loan requests.

stake(uint256).details: Caller must be the manager.      Stake amount must be non zero.      An appropriate spend limit must be present at the token contract.

unstake(uint256).details: Caller must be the manager.      Unstake amount must be non zero and not exceed amountUnstakable().

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdrawal amount must be non zero and not exceed amountWithdrawable().      Caller must not be any of: manager, protocol, current borrower.

withdrawProtocolEarnings().details: protocolEarningsOf(msg.sender) must be greater than 0.      Caller's all accumulated earnings will be withdrawn.
